{"tid":1018661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（愛回家）計劃火星移民的公司宣告破產 曾有一萬多中国人報名","createTime":"2019-02-12T11:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T23:19:49.000Z","uid":184679,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e679a39e9b147b681f93937bae80f241d84858","tid":1018661,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:39:55.000Z","msg":"2月11日福布斯報導，曾計劃將人類送上火星的Mars One公司已於1月15日宣布破產，2012年Mars One開啟火星移民計劃，原計劃於2023年在火星建立永久殖民地。一直以來，該計劃也受到一些媒體和學者的質疑，認為這很可能是一場商業騙局。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20190212/30014084.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.news.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20190212%2F30014084.html&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIurM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=51a8a215\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20190212/30014084.html</a>"},{"pid":"275cbc7aa4f5b623e16ba7f740bedc77764b2aa6","tid":1018661,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:48:35.000Z","msg":"完美呃支那豬金錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc090504599b055a24e55566f9704a14bfe02cb","tid":1018661,"uid":103230,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:49:55.000Z","msg":"點會有人信？<br />\n而家連月球都未有基地"},{"pid":"efe5f0e0dc9e08c85d51ad82e9b66d602bf19abb","tid":1018661,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:51:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Impossible!<br />\nImpossible!<br />\nImpossible!<br />\nImpossible!<br />\nImpossible!<br />\nImpossible!<br />\nIt is possible!</span></span>"},{"pid":"e11e9476e9f0f3b874f71e13362d1a030077b2a1","tid":1018661,"uid":76705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:01:04.000Z","msg":"In spacex we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b6aa684e524a726502cc9fe61b37c5eab666d7","tid":1018661,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislik